misc check the weather with data rich output: curl 'wttr.in/<location>?format=v2'
misc check the weather without colros: curl 'wttr.in/<location>?T'
misc check the weather: curl 'wttr.in/<location>'
misc dtrace debug processes of bash script: sudo dtrace -n 'proc:::exec-success /progenyof($target)/ { trace(curpsinfo->pr_psargs); }' -c <path-to-script>
misc help for checking the weather: curl 'wttr.in/:help'
misc transform from no case to snake-case: echo '<input>' | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]' | tr -cs '[:alnum:]' '_' | sed 's/^_//; s/_$//'
misc transform from no case to snake-case and copy to mac clipboard: echo '<input>' | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]' | tr -cs '[:alnum:]' '_' | sed 's/^_//; s/_$//' | pbcopy
